      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 represents a superlative example of BMW M-Division engineering. The S54 3.2L inline-six is in peak mechanical health, featuring a fully serviced double-VANOS unit and individual throttle bodies that ensure immediate transient response across the 8,000 RPM powerband. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock with zero lash. The chassis is structurally immaculate, benefiting from preventative rear subframe reinforcement and a suspension system with factory-spec bushings that maintain original kinematic precision. This vehicle is free of any mechanical or cosmetic compromises, offering a turn-key experience for the most discerning purist.",
